name: NISSAN Skyline GT-R R34 car LORA
description:
This LORA can make a car more like the NISSAN Skyline GT-R R34

When I use prompt like “GT-R” or “NISSAN GTR” to describe a car, the picture always turn out a GT-R R35.

I just love the R34, so I train this to make picture better!

It's still on testing, looks work well in some anime style models. And I hope you use this to create more beautiful works.

Thanks!

介个 LORA 能让你跑出来的日产 GT-R 更像 R34

每次关键词里面填GT-R都出来的是R35，（估计是被喂多了=_=），就做了个 LORA 来添加一点小小的 R34 震撼，目前我放在一些动漫风格的底子里跑起来还真不错，希望大家来炼一炼，提提意见。

谢谢大家！
